"<li style=\" font-family:\'Courier New\'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\">Check \'hex mode\' to show all data as space separated bytes;</li>\n"
