"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Arial\'; font-size:14pt; color:#434343; background-color:transparent;\">Data field</span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Arial\'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\">All received data are shown in this field. The data are decoded using ASCII. You may choose the format of representation for decode errors or symbols with the code value greater  than 127 (ignore, mark  symbols with the red color or decode with Win-1251). Additionally this field may contain transmitted data, timestamps or bytecodes (see Settings for more). </span></p>\n"
