"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Arial\'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\">Мacro commands can be used as shortcuts to certain commands. These commands have their own \'send\' buttons. Each macro command has its name written on a corresponding button and a command text that is sent to the active serial port after the button is selected. The set of commands comprising all 30 buttons is called macros set. You may have any number of macros sets and switch between them during a session. All macros sets are saved to the &quot;macros.json&quot; file. </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"><br /></span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Arial\'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\">The main terminal form comprises the following: </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"><br /></span></p>\n"
"<ul style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;\"><li style=\" font-family:\'Courier New\'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\">Combobox with available macros sets (loaded from &quot;Macros.json&quot; file at app start). Choose the current set here; </li>\n"
"<li style=\" font-family:\'Courier New\'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\">Thirty buttons for selected macros set commands. Each button caption is macro name. You may see macro command text on hover button tooltip. Click this button to send command text to the selected serial port. If macros set has less then 30 commands, some buttons are disabled and labelled as &lt;Not used&gt;;</li>\n"
"<li style=\" font-family:\'Courier New\'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\">\'Create/Edit macros Set\' button opens macros sets editing window. </li></ul>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"><br /></span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Arial\'; font-size:20pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\">Settings</span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Arial\'; font-size:14pt; color:#434343; background-color:transparent;\">Port Settings</span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"><br /></span></p>\n"
