"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"><br /></span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Arial\'; font-size:14pt; color:#434343; background-color:transparent;\">Text Settings</span></p>\n"
"<ul style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;\"><li style=\" font-family:\'Courier New\'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\">\'CR = LF\' — checkbox for correct end of string processing;</li>\n"
"<li style=\" font-family:\'Courier New\'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\">\'Use bytecodes\' — checkbox for finding hex codes  $00 — $FF  in transmit data and transmit them as codes;</li>\n"
"<li style=\" font-family:\'Courier New\'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\">\'Show timestamp\' —show timestamp of received data for each line in package;</li>\n"
"<li style=\" font-family:\'Courier New\'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\">\'Scroll\'— check this to scroll data field to last line after data adding;</li>\n"
"<li style=\" font-family:\'Courier New\'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\">\'Show sent\' — check this setting to include sent data into the data field;</li></ul>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"><br /></span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Arial\'; font-size:14pt; color:#434343; background-color:transparent;\">CRC parameters</span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Arial\'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\">Quetima gets CRC16 for selected file using 4129 as default polynom and 0 as init value. For changing these parameters use ‘Polynom’ and ‘StartValue’ fields </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"><br /></span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Arial\'; font-size:14pt; color:#434343; background-color:transparent;\">TextField Settings</span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"><br /></span></p>\n"
"<ul style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;\"><li style=\" font-family:\'Courier New\'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\">\'Select Font Style\'  —  selects font family and color;</li>\n"
"<li style=\" font-family:\'Courier New\'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\">\'Background color\' — selects data field text background color;</li>\n"
"<li style=\" font-family:\'Courier New\'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\">\'Font Sent Color\' — selects font color for transmitted text;</li>\n"
"<li style=\" font-family:\'Courier New\'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\">\'Font Received Color\' — selects font color for received text;</li>\n"
"<li style=\" font-family:\'Courier New\'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\">\'Bytecodes color\' — selects color for bytecodes if the bytecodes setting is enabled. </li></ul>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"><br /></span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Arial\'; font-size:20pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\">Macros sets</span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Arial\'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\">Some commands are used constantly, and it is convenient to have some buttons for quick access. These commands are called macros. 30 buttons are available. All 30 macros are grouped into a macros set. Macros sets are created in a separate window and saved to macros.json file. You may select different macros sets during one session. </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"><br /></span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Arial\'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\">The main window contains a combobox for selecting a current macros set, a macros creation window opening button and buttons for the current macros set. </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Arial\'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\">The macro name is shown on the corresponding macro button, and the command is shown on the button hover. Unused buttons are disabled and labelled as ‘not used\'.</span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"><br /></span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Arial\'; font-size:16pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\">MacrosSet Form</span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Arial\'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\">The MacrosSet Form includes the following:</span></p>\n"
"<ul style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;\"><li style=\" font-family:\'Courier New\'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\">The name of a new macros set or a selected one;</li>\n"
"<li style=\" font-family:\'Courier New\'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\">The list of available macros sets;</li>\n"
"<li style=\" font-family:\'Courier New\'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\"> The button for saving and instantly applying the current macros set;</li>\n"
"<li style=\" font-family:\'Courier New\'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\">The button for saving current macros set without applying;</li>\n"
"<li style=\" font-family:\'Courier New\'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\">The button for deleting the current macros set;</li>\n"
"<li style=\" font-family:\'Courier New\'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\">Thirty macro names combined with corresponding commands and \'Send\' buttons. Selecting a \'Send\' button results in sending the corresponding macro command to the  serial port.</li></ul>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:1; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%; background-color:transparent;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Courier New\'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Arial\'; font-size:14pt; color:#434343; background-color:transparent;\">Macros Set Creation</span></p>\n"
"<p style=\"-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><br /></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Arial\'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\">Enter the new macros set name into the «Name of Macros Set» field.</span></p>\n"
"<p style=\"-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><br /></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Arial\'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\">For each macros, enter its short name and the appropriate send command in corresponding fields. The short  name will be shown on the macros button. You may test your command by sending it immediately to the serial port using the \'Send\' button.</span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"><br /></span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Arial\'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\">You may save new macros set using \'Save\' button. To apply the new macros set and use it as a current macros set immediately, select \'Save and Apply\'. </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"><br /></span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Arial\'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\">You may edit existing macros sets the same way. </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"><br /></span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Arial\'; font-size:20pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\">Data graphs. </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Arial\'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\">Select \'Show Graph\' to start showing the data graph in a separate window.  Within this mode, every new data string is considered as a data set. The appropriate data format is</span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"><br /></span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Arial\'; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\">x; y1; y2; y3 ;…;\\r</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Arial\'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\">,</span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"><br /></span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Arial\'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\">where:</span></p>\n"
"<ul style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;\"><li style=\" font-family:\'Courier New\'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\">each data string should contain several numbers separated with semicolon;</li>\n"
"<li style=\" font-family:\'Courier New\'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\">the first number is considered as X value;</li>\n"
"<li style=\" font-family:\'Courier New\'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\">other numbers are considered as Y values;</li>\n"
"<li style=\" font-family:\'Courier New\'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\">the string may contain several Y values, but their number must be the same for all data shown on the current graph;</li>\n"
"<li style=\" font-family:\'Courier New\'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\">the data string ends with \'\\r\';</li>\n"
"<li style=\" font-family:\'Courier New\'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\">spaces are ignored. </li></ul>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Arial\'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\">Points are added to the graph after every new data string is received. Select \'Stop graph\' to exit graph mode. </span></p>\n"
