"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Arial\'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\">— Настройки подключения, внешнего вида, отправки данных;</span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Arial\'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;\">— Hex-формат;</span></p>\n"
